## Careful mode

For high-risk work (auth/billing/migrations/payments/data deletion), Lead
manually escalates per-turn:

- Run all 5 simplicity questions explicitly before every commit
- Run all 5 test questions explicitly
- Delegate to `qa-tester` + `security-engineer` (or `universal-reviewer`) for
  the diff before commit
- Smaller increments: ≤3 files per commit, not ≤5
- Mandatory peer review even for small diffs
